{"title":"夜播小麦","authors":["禾波"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":11,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜播小麦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无边的夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁静的夜啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种机的灯光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照着大地如银白。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机声隆隆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震撼田野；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒着微寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们正在播种小麦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种机开动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜鸟惊异地叫唤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万粒种籽啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却安详地躺在地上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕夜凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕风霜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了丰产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们抢夺着播种时光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦种播完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心情舒畅；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播下麦种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也播下美丽的希望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想到丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便想到连天的麦浪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬头望天上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，一片斑斓的星光。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}